j}}\n* Low German: {{tt|nds|Orange|n}}\n* Luxembourgish: {{tt|lb|Orange|f}}\n* Macedonian: {{tt|mk|портокалова|m}}\n* Malagasy: {{tt+|mg|laoranjy}}, {{tt|mg|volom-boasary}}\n* Malay: {{tt+|ms|jingga}}, {{t+|ms|oren}}\n* Malayalam: {{tt+|ml|ഓറഞ്ച്}}\n* Maltese: {{tt+|mt|oranġjo}}\n* Māori: {{tt+|mi|karaka}}\n* Marathi: {{tt|mr|नारिंगी|n}}\n* Mongolian:\n*: Cyrillic: {{tt|mn|улбар шар}}\n* Nama: {{tt|naq|oranje}}\n* Navajo: {{tt|nv|łichxíʼí}}\n* Nepali: {{tt|ne|सुन्तला रगको}}\n* Norwegian:\n*: Bokmål: {{tt+|nb|oransje|m}}\n* Occitan: {{tt+|oc|irange}}\n* Old English: {{tt|ang|geoluread}}, {{tt|ang|æppelfealu}}\n* Ossetian: {{t|os|оранжевӕ}}\n* Pashto: {{tt+|ps|نارنجي|tr=nārënji}}\n* Persian:\n*: Iranian Persian: {{tt|fa-ira|نارَنْجی}}\n* Polish: {{tt+|pl|pomarańczowy}}, {{tt+|pl|pomarańcz|m-in}}\n* Portuguese: {{tt+|pt|alaranjado|m}}, {{tt+|pt|cor-de-laranja|f}}, {{tt+|pt|laranja|m}}\n* Quechua: {{tt|qu|killmu}}, {{tt|qu|willapi}}\n* Réunion Creole French: {{t|rcf|oranj|m}}\n* Romanian: {{tt+|ro|portocaliu|n}}, {{tt+|ro|oranj|n}}\n* Russian: {{tt|ru|ора́нжевый цвет|m}}, {{tt+|ru|ора́нжевый|m}}\n* Sami:\n*: Northern Sami: {{tt|se|oránša}}\n* Samoan: {{tt|sm|lanumoli}}\n* Sardinian: {{tt|sc|colore de aranzu}}, {{tt|sc|ruggiu}}, {{tt|sc|ruiu}}, {{tt|sc|arrubiu}}\n* Scottish Gaelic: {{t|gd|orainds}}\n* Serbo-Croatian:\n*: Cyrillic: {{tt|sh|наранџаста|f}}, {{tt|sh|наранчаста|f}}\n*: Latin: {{tt|sh|narandžasta|f}}, {{tt+|sh|narančasta|f}}\n* Shona: {{tt|sn|ranjisi}}\n* Sicilian: {{tt|scn|aranciuni|m}}\n* Sindhi: {{tt+|sd|نارنگِي|tr=narangi}}\n* Sinhalese: {{t+|si|තැඹිලි}}\n* Slovak: {{tt|sk|oranžový}}\n* Slovene: {{tt|sl|oranžna|f}}, {{tt|sl|oranžna}}\n* Somali: {{tt+|so|jaalle}}\n* Spanish: {{tt+|es|naranja|m}}, {{tt+|es|anaranjado|m}}\n* Swahili: {{tt|sw|rangi ya machungwa}}\n* Swedish: {{tt+|sv|orange}}, {{tt+|sv|brandgul}}\n* Tagalog: {{tt|tl|pulaw}}, {{tt|tl|kulay-kahel}}, {{tt+|tl|kahel}}\n* Tahitian: {{tt|ty|puātou}}\n* Tajik: {{tt+|tg|норанҷӣ}}\n* Tamil: {{tt+|ta|செ